data.description: This hard to find delightful townhouse with 2BR + OFFICE or 3rd bedroom, 2.5BA in a gated community brings you HOME to a quiet location and amazingly easy, daily living. Immaculate Home. Enjoy the open, spacious floor plan on first floor with nice kitchen + dining room. New carpet throughout. All BR upstairs with 1 bathroom located in 1st floor for guests' easy accessibility. Primary BR has large en-suite, dual sinks + walk-in closet. 2nd BR and the office/bonus room have separate but immediate access to the outdoors for those clear, blue and sunny California skies in your own private veranda. Separate laundry room, washer/dryer included + 2 car attached garage. Enjoy a private, enclosed front patio and area gardening. Excellently located close to schools, shopping (Brea Mall), cluster of excellent restaurants, parks, arts + entertainment venues (Knott's Berry Farm is 3.5mi away, 5mi to Cal State Fullerton and a mere 25mi to Manhattan Beach). A can't miss, must see property!
